c: 3
v: 81
t: "Yeroo Rabbiin nabiyyoota irraa “waan ani kitaabaafi ogummaa irraa isiniif kennee, ergasii ergamaan waan isinii wajjin jiru dhugoomsu isinitti dhufe, akka isatti amantaniifi isa tumsitanu” (jechuun) waadaa qabate [yaadadhu](Rabbiinis) \"mirkaneessitanii? Sana irrattis waadaa kiyya qabdanii?\" jedhe[Isaan] \"mirkaneessine\" jedhan; (Rabbiinis) “Ragaa ta’aa; anis warra isinii wajjin ragaa ta’u irraayi” jedhe"